title: Abadabad - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description:
The single "Take It Slow" by Abadabad is this week's "Track of the Week". The band came to Converse Rubber Tracks and jumped into setting up their instruments with the aid of the studio engineers. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
